        "subject": "LU-7585 zfs: maintain index file size",
        "message": "LU-7585 zfs: maintain index file size\n\nOriginally, the index file size is always 2, then the user space\narchive tool, such as 'tar', can not work on lustre ZFS backend.\n\nThis patch maintains the index file size based on its block size\nand block count information.\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <fan.yong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ibfe03c8388438ccedaa1e4ef583ba6019d760db1\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
